title: Birthday Cannoli By BAMS
description: Birthday Cannoli by Bam’s Cannoli is profiled to taste like the delicious birthday treat of a perfectly baked cannoli with rich vanilla icing covered in festive rainbow sprinkles. The inhale of this sweet vape juice meets you with the delicious, melt in your mouth flavor of a cannoli covered in perfect vanilla icing. The exhale brings forth the sprinkle notions with a sweet and creamy whipped cream flavor sensation.  Flavor Profile: Cannoli, Vanilla Icing, Sprinkles, Whipped CreamVG/PG: 70/30Nicotine Level: 0MG, 3MG, 6MGBottle Size: 100ML
